  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00001",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 1,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "捕役押闻仁同上。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00002",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "愁城一望无边际，走遍吴头并楚岐。黑地冤枉无伸诉，问天何时是了期。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00003",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "我，闻道泉。蒙都察院老爷开恩，押我寻访娘子与百花羞下落。将及一月，可怜走遍天涯，哪里寻个踪迹。哎呀，天皇吓我并不曾为非作歹，平白的遭这无头横祸。好苦吓！",
      "text_length": 76
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00004",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "捕役"
      ],
      "text": "你也不必怨苦，好歹往前途寻问一番。若再没有，限期已满。要去回都老爷的话了。",
      "text_length": 37
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00005",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "大哥之言有理。皇天！我闻道泉受此无辜，怎不开眼一看哪！",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00006",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "平白飞灾来缠累，叫天不应泪空垂。夙世结下冤仇对，到得今生受灾危。无辜委屈受鞭捶，披锁监押访娥眉。访得消息宽追逼，不然一命难免轮回。",
      "text_length": 65
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00007",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "闻仁、捕役同下。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00008",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "孙悟空、猪悟能同上。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00009",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "下山虎",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "驾云迅逝，急走如驰。渡海三千里，救师岂肯迟。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00010",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "呀！忽然冤气冲天。兄弟，这冤气有些缘故。https://scripts.xikao.com/play/020060362021-07-21",
      "text_length": 69
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00011",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "下山虎",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "待我去探取缘由，相度事宜。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00012",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪悟能"
      ],
      "text": "哥哥，我们去救师父要紧，别样事儿，不要管他罢。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00013",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "下山虎",
      "speakers": [
        "猪悟能"
      ],
      "text": "休戚无关同水米，俺师父方如渴慕梅。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00014",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪悟能"
      ],
      "text": "我和你在此地，哪里不知怎么着急。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00015",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "兄弟，你不晓得。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00016",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "下山虎",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "这里行程须仔细，不用多疑忌事非。两歧好待，相逢生转机。",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00017",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "孙悟空、猪悟能同下。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00018",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "捕役押闻仁同上。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00019",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "两腿疼痛步难挪，道路泥滑似滂沱。思之偷生不如死，瞑目九泉待如何？",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00020",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "闻仁撞。孙悟空、猪悟能同上。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00021",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "那汉子为着何事，带锁披枷，寻此短见？",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00022",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "捕役、闻仁同怕。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00023",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "不要怕。我们是大唐天子差往西天取经的圣僧徒弟。我乃孙悟空，他叫猪悟能。你有什么冤情，对我们讲了。自然还你个明白。",
      "text_length": 56
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00024",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "二位，小生闻仁。为了功名携妻上京。不期有个柏大将军呵！",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00025",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "只为元宵春灯谜。千金披卷把祸移。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00026",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空",
        "猪悟能"
      ],
      "text": "可是百花羞么？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00027",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "正是。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00028",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空",
        "猪悟能"
      ],
      "text": "你为何这等狼狈？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00029",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "师父莫非知来历，这场冤屈世间稀。我同妻子进京地，惹得捕役心带疑。不分皂白来拿住，三敲六问受鞭笞。",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00030",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "那捕役将我等拿住，道我妻子，就是百花羞。被我用什么邪术，将他们来藏匿过了。",
      "text_length": 37
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00031",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空",
        "猪悟能"
      ],
      "text": "你不见妻子之时，正遇着那捕人？",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00032",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "正是。可怜吓！不分皂白，将我拿到官去。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00033",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "是谁押你去访觅？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00034",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "我的罪案已呈圣上，恐有含冤，批与都察院复勘。蒙那老爷审出情由，奈无实迹，不便回旨。赏了路费，差这位解哥押我访寻。可怜哪！",
      "text_length": 60
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00035",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "无踪迹，夫妻两地无会期。无奈只得寻死地，幸遇慈悲救残躯。",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00036",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "好。我与你有缘，我二人也是为百花羞一事而来。你妻子下落，我已知道了。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00037",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "管叫你雾散云开，重现出一轮蟾桂。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00038",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "师父既知我妻子下落，几时才得相会？https://scripts.xikao.com/play/020060362021-07-21",
      "text_length": 66
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00039",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "就在目下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00040",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪悟能"
      ],
      "text": "住了。你即是闻道泉么？",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00041",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "正是。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00042",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪悟能"
      ],
      "text": "哥哥，事有凑巧。师父蒙百花羞放走，有书两封，一封是百花羞寄与父母，一封是闻道泉之妻，寄与他丈夫的。",
      "text_length": 49
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00043",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "我说其中有奇。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00044",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪悟能"
      ],
      "text": "哥哥果有先见之明。服你，服你。闻生请看书。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00045",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "猪悟能递书，闻仁看。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00046",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "妻吓！果然是妻子手笔。二位大恩人，请上受我一拜。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00047",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空",
        "猪悟能"
      ],
      "text": "不消，不消。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00048",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "如今妻子已有了下落。并听得说什么百花羞，难道就是那柏大将军的女儿么？",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00049",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪悟能"
      ],
      "text": "怎么不是。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00050",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "闻仁"
      ],
      "text": "谢天谢地。今日得遇恩人，两桩无影无踪的事情，都得明白了。",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00051",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "不要多讲。你们都随我来。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00052",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "孙悟空、猪悟能、闻仁、捕役同走圆场。四小妖同上。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00053",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "四小妖"
      ],
      "text": "不好了！猴公公、猪爹爹来了！",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00054",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "孙悟空打死三小妖，留小妖甲捉住。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00055",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "你们老妖在家么？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00056",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "小妖甲"
      ],
      "text": "不在家，到柏将军家认丈人去了。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00057",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪悟能"
      ],
      "text": "这小妖也留不得了。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00058",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "孙悟空打死小妖甲。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00059",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "妙，都打死了。百花羞，花香洁，不知在哪里？",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00060",
      "play_id": "02006036",
      "scene_id": "02006036_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪悟能"
      ],
      "text": "那里一所精致房子，一定是妖怪的内室。打进去。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006036_e00061",
